PRETRAINED MODEL WEIGHTS
========================

The pretrained model weights released as part of this project are derived from
CroCo pretrained checkpoints (Copyright 2022-present Naver Corporation,
CC BY-NC-SA 4.0) and were further trained using the datasets documented in the
NOTICE file. Use of the pretrained weights is additionally subject to the
license terms of those upstream components and training datasets.


